WEBVTT

00:07:28.576 --> 00:07:30.748
finding a space
where they were productive.

00:07:30.772 --> 00:07:34.922
SA: One man who was
an executive coach said,

00:07:34.946 --> 00:07:37.128
"Maybe I'd wear shorts in the summer,

00:07:37.152 --> 00:07:38.310
but other than that,

00:07:38.334 --> 00:07:40.870
I'd put on some sort work-type outfit,

00:07:40.894 --> 00:07:44.268
and I'd go down to my lower-level office,

00:07:44.292 --> 00:07:46.025
and I was then 'at work.'"

00:07:46.428 --> 00:07:50.267
Another person -- she was a screenwriter,

00:07:50.291 --> 00:07:54.321
and she said, "I do all
of my creative work in my bed."

00:07:54.843 --> 00:07:57.084
AG: The second structure was routines:

00:07:57.108 --> 00:07:59.387
forming habits around a regular schedule.

00:07:59.411 --> 00:08:00.912
Like a writer who said,